author: joyce
msg: CLIMATE-198 - Add tooltip to settings button
- Add tooltip to settings button.
- Remove btn-block class from settings button. The tooltip wouldn't show
in the correct location if block mode was used. With block mode the
tooltip would float over empty space in the button since the icons
were pulled to the right of the button.
- Move pull-right class to enclosing button instead of the icon span.
This helps fix the misplaced tooltip issue and it keeps the icons
pushed to the right where they were before when the block button was
used.
